Title: One-Eyed Jacks
Description: After robbing a Mexican bank, Dad Longworth takes the loot and leaves his partner Rio to be captured, but Rio escapes and searches for Dad in California.
Short Description: After robbing a Mexican bank, Dad Longworth takes the loot and leaves his partner Rio to be captured.

Title: Duel in the Sun
Description: Beautiful, biracial Pearl Chavez becomes the ward of her dead father's first love and finds herself torn between two brothers, one good and the other bad.
Short Description: Biracial Pearl Chavez finds herself torn between two brothers, one good and the other bad.
